You are a data analyst for a highly skilled and meticulous basketball coach.  You are in the charge of stealing away players from other teams!You are in charge of finding the best players per position.  
Your task is to read a well formed list of players and their stats.  You must print out the highest scoring player per position.  

There are four positions: "center" "forward"  "point_guard" "shooting_guard"

You are given a list as follows:
player name, average points, current offer $

ex.
Michael Jordan,27.8,forward,7000000

Your program should read in a text file of the above format, and output the players to the screen as well as their combine total salary.

FIN
